      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"They think they can just walk in here and change everything? They ain't got the sense to know how this town works; they just bring their outside notions with 'em.\" One man might sneer, \"Some people just ain't built for this kind of society, see? They got their own place, and that's where they ought to stay.\" Another could chime in, \"You let 'em mix things up, and you lose all sense of who's in charge here. It's just natural, the way things are.\"",
